Title: Backfilling Postgres TOAST Columns in Debezium Data Change Events
Description:
Postgres logical replication, while powerful for capturing real-time data changes, presents challenges with TOAST columns,
whose values can be absent from data change events in specific situations.
This post discusses how Debezium addresses this through its built-in reselect post processor,
then explores more robust solutions leveraging Apache Flink‚Äôs capabilities for stateful stream processing,
including Flink SQL and the brand-new process table functions (PTFs) in Flink 2.1.
